window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Mason now has proof the Master is working in Nalnora, but he’s quickly learned that getting elves to cooperate is like herding cats. Dangerous, murderous cats.</p> <p>So, he has to take matters into his own hands...especially when the elven beauty, Deya, catches his eye.</p> <p>To keep her, and all these women, safe, Mason will have to walk a razor’s edge as he plays a dangerous political game, learns more about the power of runes, and tries to stay one step ahead of the Master.</p> <p>And to stay one step ahead, maybe it’s time he upgrade his method of transportation....</p>"; 
